WittyPad is a a free, open source knowledge-management community portal. WittyPad will be available under the http://wittypad.com.
WittyPad developer blog is available under http://wittypadblog.blogspot.com.
Follow WittyPad on twitter: @wittypad

 1 Running Witty
 ===============
 Witty communities are working with sub domains, so to run witty in development mode, you should modify your host
 settings.
 Corresponding to grails.serverURL and grails.serverName properties in the Config.groovy you should add the following
 lines to your hosts file:
 127.0.0.1              wittypad.local              #Witty home page, desktop layout
 127.0.0.1				m.wittypad.local            #Witty home page, mobile layout
 127.0.0.1				witty.wittypad.local        #Witty community, desktop layout
 127.0.0.1				m.witty.wittypad.local      #Witty community, mobile layout

